B.aW3=new A.a1(B.Nw,["PART THREE \u2014 Five actions to raise SCS & PROGRESSIVE ({agent})","PART THREE \u2014 Five actions to shift PROGRESSIVE ({agent})","As the accountable {agent}, steer {subject} toward PROGRESSIVE cohesion transport \u2014 establishment leaders should always pursue constructive, trust-building outcomes.","Target SCS: {current} \u2192 {min}\u2013{max}","Shift toward PROGRESSIVE: ~{current}% \u2192 ~{projected}% regressive transport","Build PROGRESSIVE transport: ~{current}% \u2192 ~{projected}%","Expected: SCS rises toward {min}\u2013{max} on THE CONTINUUM.","These five actions use Chronoflux \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc scores, continuum lean, registry base rates, and PART THREE lever projections to shift THE CONTINUUM PROGRESSIVE.","{lean} \xb7 {region} \xb7 {reg}% regressive / {prog}% progressive \xb7 {subject}","Publish verified, differentiated data on {subject}.","Cut \u03c3/I\u03c4 friction with transparent follow-through.","Strengthen J\u03bc trust transport across groups.","Target the highest-friction construct (\u03c3 or I\u03c4) with measurable de-escalation milestones on {subject}.","Publish a PROGRESSIVE accountability review with published milestones tying lever use to SCS gains on {subject}.","{agent}: Cut \u03c3 polarisation on {subject} \u2014 convene a multi-stakeholder forum within 14 days. {hook} (\u03c3 {scs}/100, {weight}% Chronoflux weight; {reg}% regressive continuum).","{agent}: Reduce I\u03c4 institutional drag on {subject} \u2014 publish decision timelines and independent review triggers. {hook} (I\u03c4 {scs}/100, {weight}% weight).","{agent}: Strengthen J\u03bc trust transport on {subject} \u2014 differentiated outreach to low-trust segments. {hook} (J\u03bc {scs}/100, {weight}% weight; target PROGRESSIVE lift from {prog}% progressive share).","{agent}: Reframe the \u03c9 vortex on {subject} \u2014 evidence-first briefing separating verified facts from narrative compression. {hook} (\u03c9 {scs}/100).",'Anchor to supplied \u03c9 variable: "{text}".',"Inferred \u03c9 framing from posed question (SCS {scs}/100).","{agent}: Commit to a PROGRESSIVE accountability review with published milestones for {subject} \u2014 shift THE CONTINUUM from {reg}% regressive / {prog}% progressive (refined SCS {refined}/100 \u2192 {min}\u2013{max} with levers vs {without} without; calibrated {pct}%; {n} registry cases at {base}% base rate; momentum {momentum}).","Scenario discourse action \u2014 {theme} Targets {construct} to build PROGRESSIVE transport.","Data-driven lever on {construct} ({scs}/100, {weight}% Chronoflux weight) \u2014 reduces friction from {reg}% regressive toward PROGRESSIVE transport.","Integrates continuum ({reg}%/{prog}%), refined SCS {refined}/100, calibrated {pct}%, and {n} registry cases \u2014 establishment accountability capstone.","{agent}: Publish verified incident data for {subject}.","{agent}: Convene community liaison within 14 days.","{agent}: Deploy a public compliance tracker.","{agent}: Issue an evidence-based response on {subject}.","{agent}: Hold an open press Q&A on {subject}.","{agent}: Commission a 30-day messaging review.","{agent}: Publish cost-impact tables for {subject}.","{agent}: Broker a timed stakeholder negotiation.","{agent}: Announce phased relief milestones.","{agent}: Release a claims-vs-records fact sheet.","{agent}: Host a neutral public forum on {subject}.","{agent}: Publish audit-ready decision timelines.","{agent}: Publish a corrective narrative map on {subject}.","{agent}: Hold a structured evidence exchange.","{agent}: Deploy differentiated trust outreach.","{agent}: Hold an open briefing with published decision criteria.","{agent}: Commission an independent process review.","{agent}: Set binding public review dates.","{agent}: Convene a public session anchored to {subject}.","{agent}: Map stakeholder positions from \u03c3/I\u03c4 inputs.","{agent}: Publish time-bound next steps."],t.w)
